  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Needle size from22 to 25 were used for fine needle aspiration of palpable breast lumps. In
      this study we choose one, randomly, and fallow the result of cytologic evaluation regarding
      specimen adequacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patient assigned randomly to FNA of palpable breast mass with different needle
      size:21-22-23-24
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
